Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.86,0:01:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,看在小羊羔的份上  你在做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What in the name of little billy goats are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.31,0:01:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我醒得早  再也睡不着了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I woke up early and I couldn't go back to sleep,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.91,0:01:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,所以在读你的小说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}so I started reading your novel.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.91,0:01:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,等等  就快看完了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hold on. I'm almost finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.72,0:01:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,可我还没写完呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, I-I on the other hand am nowhere near finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.99,0:01:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,有些早期场景故意遗漏了上下文\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Um, you know, several early scenes lack context intentionally,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.68,0:01:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我将在未完成的后续章节中补坑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}which will be made clear in the subsequent and as-of-now-unwritten chapters --
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.69,0:01:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,嘘\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Shh!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.13,0:01:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是想亡羊补牢  降低你的期望\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm merely just trying to retroactively manage your expectations is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.65,0:01:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我很喜欢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.53,0:01:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我真为你骄傲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And I'm really proud of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.65,0:01:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我上班要迟到了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, I'm gonna be late for work.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.92,0:02:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,知道吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You know,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.66,0:02:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我昨天去磨刀时想到了你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}uh, I was thinking about you yesterday while I was getting my knives sharpened, and --
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.90,0:02:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我应该担心吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Should I be alarmed here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.62,0:02:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我的想法当然没有杀意\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Uh, no. The thought which sprang to mind was decidedly not homicidal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.25,0:02:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,总之  那个刀匠正好也配钥匙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}At any rate, this particular cutler also happens to be a key cutter.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.07,0:02:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我很想多见见你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I want to very much see more of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.83,0:02:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,近来你工作很忙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And with your job taking up so much of your time as of late,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.28,0:02:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我想着这样更方便\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I just figured this might make things a little bit easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.75,0:02:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,以防我没说清  这是我公寓的钥匙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}In case it is not clear, it is a key to my apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.05,0:02:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,史蒂芬妮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Stephanie,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.00,0:02:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I love you.
