Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.74,0:03:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,顺利吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So, things went well?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.28,0:03:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,实话说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, to put it bluntly,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.76,0:03:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我五点半要和她一起吃冰淇淋\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm meeting her for ice cream at 17:30,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.76,0:03:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我仍然不知道接下来该做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and I'm still uncertain as to my follow-up move.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.18,0:03:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,但我能意识到  这是个积极的结果\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But I can recognize that what transpired was a positive outcome.
