Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.52,0:03:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,所以无法想象接下来会发生什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I cannot hold it conceivable what comes next.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.99,0:03:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你爱她吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do you love her?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.19,0:03:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,那当然\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A strong affirmative.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.00,0:03:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,她说她也爱我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And she has said that she reciprocates.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.84,0:03:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,那就放松吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Then relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.26,0:03:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我是认真的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.40,0:03:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,当一个女人说爱你时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}When a woman tells you that she loves you,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.90,0:03:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,相信她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}believe her.
