Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.36,0:06:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我是尤金\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's Eugene.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.88,0:06:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你在家吗  史蒂芬妮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Are you in there, Stephanie?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.85,0:07:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,看起来挺好  印吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Looks good. Put it to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.82,0:07:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,等等\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.56,0:07:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,她说看起来不好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}She says it doesn't look good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.88,0:07:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,这句我看懂了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeah, I got that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.54,0:07:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,戴维斯士兵有故事要说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"Trooper Davis has a story to tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.56,0:07:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,他不会冒着被逐出联邦的风险\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He wouldn't risk getting kicked out of Commonwealth
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.31,0:07:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,无缘无故做这种事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}for no reason."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.57,0:07:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,没错  有缘故\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's right. He didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.13,0:07:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,他的医生证实了他有创伤后遗症\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We have a statement from his doctors backing up his PTSD claim.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.87,0:07:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,得了吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.63,0:07:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,军医的话和军方指挥部的话一样不可信\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't trust the military doctors any more than I trust the military command.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.36,0:07:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,泰勒·戴维斯遭遇了某件事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Something happened to Tyler Davis.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.48,0:07:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,某件他认为错在弥尔顿总管\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Something that he blames Governor Milton for.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.49,0:08:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,并值得去公开质疑她的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Something worth confronting her in public over.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.52,0:08:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,而他们显然因为某种理由在隐瞒真相\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And they clearly have a reason for suppressing the truth."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.24,0:08:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一种解释\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's one interpretation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.05,0:08:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,另一种解释是泰勒·戴维斯有心理疾病\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The other is that Tyler Davis had a mental-health crisis.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.66,0:08:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,这两种解释中  只有一种解释有事实支撑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And only one of those interpretations has the facts to support it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.00,0:08:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,他说过还有上千个像他一样的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"He spoke of thousands more like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.62,0:08:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么意思\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.93,0:08:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我们应该...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We should be --"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.74,0:08:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我们应该印出化装舞会上真正发生了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"We should be printing what really happened at the masquerade ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.64,0:08:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,但你只想改述弥尔顿总管在通稿中的话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But, instead, you want to paraphrase what Governor Milton said in her press release."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.15,0:08:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不  康妮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, Connie.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.02,0:08:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我要你去改述弥尔顿总管在通稿中的话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I want you to paraphrase Governor Milton's press release
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.89,0:08:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,这样下次  我就不用亲自出马了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}so that the next time, I don't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.60,0:09:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,既然没人见过她  没人和她说过话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, if no one's seen her and no one's talked to her,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.22,0:09:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,那她是怎么请假的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}how can she have called in sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.99,0:09:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我从没说她请假了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I never said she did.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.25,0:09:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我只知道  我来顶班是因为她没现身\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All I know is, I was told to be here because she didn't show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.34,0:09:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,可以了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.23,0:09:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你确定要这样做吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Are you sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.18,0:09:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,那个人劫持过人质\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The guy took a hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.51,0:09:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,他当时担心自己的安危\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He was afraid for his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.37,0:09:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我也担心过自己的安危\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've been afraid for my life,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.14,0:09:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,但我从没有劫持过无辜人质\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've never taken an innocent hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.38,0:09:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是想知道他认为帕梅拉做了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I just want to know what he thinks Pamela did.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.17,0:09:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你之所以想知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The only reason you want to know
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.14,0:09:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,只是因为他们想隐瞒这件事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}is because they're trying to keep it a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.44,0:09:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,这是私人病房\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is a private room.
