Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.93,0:10:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,联邦军\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is C.A.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.72,0:10:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我们被要求检查你的安全\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We've been asked to perform a wellness check.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.88,0:10:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,请开门\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Please open the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.20,0:10:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,她不在\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}She's not there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.36,0:10:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,那我想立刻作供\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Then I'd like to make a statement immediately,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.71,0:10:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,趁我记忆犹新时  详述她最后的行踪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}recount the details of her last-knowns on the record now
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.96,0:10:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,以供记录在案\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}while this is still fresh in my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.00,0:10:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,好  来站里一趟  我帮你填文件\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sure. Come down to the station. I'll help you fill out the paperwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.53,0:11:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你常这样出行吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How often do you take trips like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.13,0:11:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,没我希望的那么频繁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Not as often as I'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.19,0:11:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这听起来可能很疯狂  但是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This probably sounds crazy, but
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.58,0:11:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我感觉比起在城市里  我在外面感觉更好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I feel like I'm better out here than I am in the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.75,0:11:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,听起来一点不疯狂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It doesn't sound crazy at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.68,0:11:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的很多人也有同感\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A lot of my people feel that way, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.08,0:11:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你仍然分你们和我们啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You still see this as your people and my people.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.07,0:11:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我想让你看这个地方是如何运作的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I want you to see how this place works,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.33,0:11:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我希望你成为它的一部分\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}because I want you to be a part of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.03,0:11:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,总的来说  我混得还不错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've done fairly well, all things considered,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.66,0:12:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,但我不是一开始就处在顶端\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but let's just say I didn't start out on the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.11,0:12:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在算处在顶端吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Is that where you are now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.32,0:12:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,勉强算吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hardly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.86,0:12:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,弥尔顿总管管理这座城市\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Governor Milton runs the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.99,0:12:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,但我知道它是如何运作的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But I know how it runs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.91,0:12:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你是从底层打拼上来的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Because you started out at the bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.75,0:12:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,很久以前  我向弥尔顿家族证明了我的能力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I proved myself to the Milton family a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.28,0:12:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你跟正确的人打交道  卡萝尔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If you're in with the right people, Carol,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.80,0:12:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你的前途不可限量\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the sky's the limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.63,0:12:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,向上爬时你会学到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And one of the things you learn as you're climbing your way up
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.77,0:12:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,任何组织内都有两种人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}is that there are two types of people in any organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.12,0:12:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,一种是佣兵\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}On the one hand, you've got the mercenaries.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.02,0:12:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,他们拿钱干活\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They're in it for the money
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.31,0:12:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,靠地位来满足自己的某种欲望\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and whatever psychological itch their position allows them to scratch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.68,0:12:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,另一种是爱国者\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And on the other, you have the patriots,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.98,0:12:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,忠诚信徒  想做好事的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the true believers, the ones who want to do good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.24,0:12:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,至于做的是不是好事也许有待商榷\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And whether they are or not might be up to debate,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.12,0:12:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,但他们加入\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but in their hearts, they're there
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.33,0:12:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,是因为他们真心相信组织\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}because they believe in the organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.20,0:12:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你让我来就是为了这个吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Is that why I'm here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.40,0:12:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,把我改造成忠诚信徒吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You want to make a true believer out of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.60,0:12:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我读过你的档案\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I read your file.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.32,0:13:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我让你来是因为你够聪明\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're here because you're smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.54,0:13:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得你能帮我应付这个混蛋\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I think you'll be able to help me deal with this asshole.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.20,0:13:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,至于你怎么想  那取决于你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What you get out of it is up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.91,0:13:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.11,0:13:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,毒贩还是走私贩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Drug dealers or smugglers?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.14,0:13:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是走私贩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're smugglers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.59,0:13:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,但这与你想的不同\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But it's not what you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.75,0:13:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,这地方严格来说不属于联邦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This place is not exactly a part of the Commonwealth,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.88,0:13:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,但我们需要他们  他们需要我们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but they need us, and we need them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.06,0:14:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我们用罂粟为医院制作鸦片\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We use the poppies to make opium for the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.18,0:14:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,如果用完了  那里的情况会变得很糟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Things will start looking pretty bleak there if we run out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.48,0:14:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我负责确保这不会发生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I make sure that doesn't happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.27,0:14:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,但有时候  我得和莫托这样的人打交道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But, sometimes, that means dealing with guys like Moto.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.44,0:14:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我说过会发生这种事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I told you what was gonna happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.40,0:14:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,而我说过你要处理好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And I asked you to manage it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.96,0:14:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我说服他们加工了最后一批货\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I talked them into processing this last batch.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.54,0:14:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我尽力了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Best I could do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.28,0:14:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我说过他们会扣下收成的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I told you they're gonna hold the harvest hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.78,0:14:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,他们要求加薪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They want a raise.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.21,0:14:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,如果不加  他们发誓让收成烂在地里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They swear they'll let it rot without one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.16,0:14:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我们来看看怎么办吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, let's see what we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.51,0:14:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是《论坛报》的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're with the Tribune.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.28,0:14:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,去2号\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're in number 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.87,0:14:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,太荒唐了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.50,0:15:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,珍知道我对警察军事化怎么看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.25,0:15:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,所以派我来写随队宣传文章
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.09,0:15:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你不想惹她生气
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.30,0:15:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,也许你应该考虑一下按她的要求办事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.22,0:15:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,就这一次
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.70,0:15:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,最近没见到你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I haven't seen you around.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.49,0:15:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你还好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How are you holding up?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.09,0:15:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,在固定范围内我还算正常\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm functioning within to-be-expected parameters.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.99,0:15:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  我看出来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeah, no, I can see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.14,0:15:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,所以能让我进去吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Uh, so can you let me in?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.45,0:15:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我带了千层面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I brought lasagna.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.49,0:16:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,盘子是空的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is an empty dish.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.26,0:16:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,对  抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, yeah, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.73,0:16:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我没做千层面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I didn't make lasagna.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.91,0:16:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,一般带食物别人都会让你进去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}People just always have to let you in if you're carrying food.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.02,0:16:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,那么  怎么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So, what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.82,0:16:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,联邦军放弃了搜索\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}When the C.A. Gave up the search,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.14,0:16:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我决定亲自调查史蒂芬妮的失踪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I decided to investigate Stephanie's disappearance myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.55,0:16:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,实话说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Truth be told,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.50,0:16:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,随着时间流逝  线索无迹可寻\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}as the hours tick by with nary a bread crumb to be found,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.25,0:16:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我被绝望吞噬了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I let my despair get the best of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.92,0:17:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,直到一次偶遇让我发现了端倪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That is, until a chance encounter put me on the trail.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.07,0:17:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sir. Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.33,0:17:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,先生  我要和你谈谈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sir, I need to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.71,0:17:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托了  我要谈谈...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Please, I need to talk --
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.46,0:17:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,雷辛街1634号\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}1634 Racine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.94,0:17:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,一号住宅区的一座公寓楼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's an apartment building in Residential One.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.15,0:17:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,三天前  你被看到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Three days ago, you were seen --
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.45,0:17:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,在晚上七点下了楼梯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}at 7:00 in the P.M., you were seen coming down the stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.55,0:17:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,-我不记得了  -等等\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- I don't remember this. - Uh, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.15,0:17:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Uh, sir, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.80,0:17:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,先生  拜托了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sir, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.86,0:17:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我的一位至亲失踪了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Someone near and dear to me has gone missing,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.54,0:17:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你也许看到了能帮我找到她的线索\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and you may have seen something that might help me find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.56,0:17:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,在哪里来着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Where was this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.52,0:18:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,一号住宅区\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Residential One.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.23,0:18:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,三天前  大概晚上七点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Three days ago, at approximately 7:00 in the P.M.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.88,0:18:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeah.
