Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.96,0:18:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不必说  我对他的说法相当怀疑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Needless to say, I greeted his story with a great deal of skepticism.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.19,0:18:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,当晚街头没有城市服务车\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There were no city service carts on the street that night,
