Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.17,0:18:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,在她失踪当晚  唯一一个在场的男人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I found it very peculiar that the one person I knew was there
