Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.72,0:19:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,他肯定不是个管道工\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And he is most definitely not a plumber.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.26,0:19:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,他通常在晚上办事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He mostly conducts his business at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.50,0:19:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,他的行动基地是仓库区的一座大楼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}His base of operations is a building in the warehouse district,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.89,0:19:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,这家公司自称是管道服务承包商\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}which purports to be a purveyor of plumbing services
