Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.96,0:19:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不过  他们从没有收到过任何邮件\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}However, they never receive any mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.75,0:19:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,非营业时间里面亮着灯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There's lights on at odd hours, when they're ostensibly closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.40,0:19:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,还有人经常进出\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And while people go in and out with a fair degree of regularity,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.89,0:19:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,通常都是同样的四个人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}it's usually just the same four people over and over.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.98,0:19:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,他们独自抵达  然后很快离开\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They usually arrive alone and depart shortly thereafter
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.59,0:19:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,经常两人一组会面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and frequently meeting in groups of two.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.22,0:20:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,只有一次全员到齐  并有第五人到场\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And on the one occasion they were all together, they were also met by a fifth,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.40,0:20:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为他就是老大\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}who I also believe to be the head honcho,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.18,0:20:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,他是政府内流氓势力的幕后黑手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the mastermind of some sort of rogue element
