Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.06,0:20:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你认为是政府的人绑架了她吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Like, you think she was kidnapped by the government or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.32,0:20:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,在我开始搜索不久之后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Shortly after I began my search,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.90,0:20:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我后来所知道的二号同谋者\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the man who later became known to me as Co-Conspirator Number Two,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.99,0:20:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是"圆帽男"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}a.K.A. "Beanie Hat Man,"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.49,0:20:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,来到了史蒂芬妮的公寓\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}showed up to Stephanie's apartment
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.05,0:20:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,带着一队搬家工  带走了她的所有东西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}with a team of movers, collected all her belongings,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.51,0:20:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,将之运去了未知地点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and took them to an unknown location.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.71,0:20:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,然后在同一天\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Then, that same day,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.73,0:20:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,史蒂芬妮在联合车站的档案中出现了这个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}this was found in Stephanie's file at Union Station.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.06,0:20:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,这是史蒂芬妮在失踪当天签的工作调动申请\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's a work-transfer request signed by Stephanie on the day of her disappearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.06,0:20:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,那天在无线电室给她顶班的男子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The man who filled in for her at the radio room
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.85,0:20:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,说她并没有提前申请过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that day told me she gave no notice whatsoever.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.78,0:20:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,没有权力机构的直接干涉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Such orders could not be falsified or fabricated
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.51,0:20:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,这种调令是不可能被篡改或伪造的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}without direct influence from within the halls of power.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.06,0:21:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,她知道他们要找她算账\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}She knew they were coming for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.45,0:21:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,在她逃跑以后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}When she eluded them,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.66,0:21:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,他们申请了假工作调动来掩盖她的失踪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}they filed that false work transfer to cover up her disappearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.94,0:21:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,为了取回她搜集的证据  他们运走了她的所有东西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They took all her belongings to recover any evidence she may have gathered,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.55,0:21:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,现在修补漏洞的最后一步只剩抹消她了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and now silencing her is the last step in repairing that leak.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.74,0:21:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我是对的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If I'm right,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.23,0:21:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,她唯一的希望\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}her only hope
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.68,0:21:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,就是我赶在他们找到她之前曝光他们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}is for me to expose them before they find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.70,0:21:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,今年渔获如何\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Good hatches this year?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.93,0:21:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,很好  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.38,0:21:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,捕了足够的鱼  我现在钓鱼只是为了娱乐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We catch enough that I can actually just do it for fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.77,0:21:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你的爱好也是一项末日技能真好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's nice when your hobby is also an apocalypse skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.89,0:21:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,说得对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Amen to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.27,0:21:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能满足他们的要求\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So, I can't give them what they want,
