Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.39,0:21:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,生产更多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Produce more,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.85,0:21:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,挣得更多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}make more.
