Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.04,0:25:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,这真的很酷\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}it's really cool, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.41,0:25:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你为她做了这么多事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You doing so much for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.91,0:25:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,删掉  重写\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Strike that. Reverse that.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.16,0:25:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是在偿还我欠她的人情\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm merely trying to repay what I owe.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.04,0:26:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,一开始  在我们都以为这场灾难\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I made a promise to myself in those early days,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.04,0:26:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,几周就会过去时  我向自己许下了一个承诺\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}back when we thought this would all blow over in a few weeks,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.08,0:26:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我能挺过去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that if I lived through this,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.41,0:26:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我会追寻梦想  成为一名科幻作家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'd pursue my dream of becoming a science-fiction author.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.96,0:26:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我在无线电里  开玩笑地跟史蒂芬妮说过这事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I have jokingly related that story to Stephanie over the radio.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.96,0:26:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,她告诉我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And she told me,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.66,0:26:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能等到挺过去以后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"You can't wait till after you've lived through it,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.46,0:26:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,因为不管你有没有准备好  我们都只拥有当下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}'cause ready or not, right now is all we've got."
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.16,0:26:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,她给了我勇气去做我一直想做的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}She gave me the courage to do something I've always wanted to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.75,0:26:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,如果有人能帮你做到这点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and when someone can do that for you, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.08,0:26:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,连"爱"这个词都显得不够用了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...words like love seem insufficient.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.08,0:27:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,该死\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.96,0:27:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,上吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.62,0:27:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你想闯进他的公寓吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You want to break into his apartment?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.50,0:27:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.08,0:27:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想惹麻烦  尤金\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't want to get in trouble, Eugene.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.58,0:27:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我有份小工作  有张小床\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I got a little job. I got a little bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.96,0:27:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我可能还会养只小猫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I might get a little cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.71,0:27:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,这太不妙了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.58,0:27:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,他每周二都要跑十英里  雷打不动\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}His Tuesday 10-mile is ironclad.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.54,0:27:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,他会离开九十分钟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He'll be gone for 90 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.00,0:27:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.41,0:27:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,公主\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Princess,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.66,0:27:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,他是解答一切的关键  我知道的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}he's the key to cracking this whole thing wide open. I just know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.00,0:27:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉不能留下吃炸鱼了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sorry we can't stay for the fish fry.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.75,0:27:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,下次吧  朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Next time, my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.29,0:27:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,好  一言为定\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeah, deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.16,0:27:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么看\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.50,0:28:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,他在剥削他们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's robbing them.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.75,0:28:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我和其中一个小队长谈了谈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I talked to one of the lieutenants.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.75,0:28:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,他私吞了你给他们加薪的钱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's pocketing the money that you give them for raises
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.04,0:28:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,并殴打他们  让他们保持沉默\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and beating them to keep quiet about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.25,0:28:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,他前晚做得太过了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He went too far the other night,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.37,0:28:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,所以他们才会罢工\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and that's why they're on strike.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.96,0:28:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,他们会拿回自己的钱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They'll get their money back
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.04,0:28:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我答应的加薪也不会少\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and the raise I just promised them.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.33,0:28:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,莫托怎么处理\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What about Moto?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.87,0:28:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我是不会再和他一起钓鱼了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, I'm not gonna go fishing with him anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.41,0:28:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,这点是肯定的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.16,0:28:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,现在就拘留他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Take him into custody now.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.54,0:28:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,搞什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hey! What -- What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.25,0:28:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,别碰我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Get your hands off of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.21,0:28:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,霍恩斯比\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hornsby!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.08,0:28:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你这个娘娘腔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You mother-pussbucket!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.79,0:29:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,尤金\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hey, Eugene?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.54,0:29:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,他跑十英里时下雨了会怎么做\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What's this guy do when it rains on his 10-mile run?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.79,0:29:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,鉴于最近缺少降雨\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, given our recent lack of precipitation,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.33,0:29:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我还没有这个信息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've not yet gathered that data.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.04,0:29:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,现在有了  他回来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, you have now. He's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.46,0:29:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得离开了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We have to get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.25,0:29:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,报告他的距离\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Count off his range.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.25,0:29:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.25,0:29:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,他的距离  五十  四十  三十\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}His range -- 50, 40, 30.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.33,0:29:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我不擅长这个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm not good at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.62,0:29:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我还剩多少时间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Just tell me how much time I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.62,0:29:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,哥们  我说了还剩多少时间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Dude, I am telling you how much time you have,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.87,0:30:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你没时间了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and you have no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.00,0:30:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我看到他们在外面的梯子上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I saw them on the ladder outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.00,0:30:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能跑远的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Couldn't have gotten that far.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.46,0:30:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,他们在那里  就是他们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hey! There they are! That's them!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.96,0:30:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,墨瑟将军  能为你做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}General Mercer, how can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.04,0:30:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,33号房的病人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Where is the patient who was in M-33
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.37,0:30:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,和看守他的士兵去哪了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and the soldiers that were with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.58,0:30:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,33号房没有病人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There's no one in M-33.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.46,0:31:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I realize that.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.50,0:31:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我想问的是  之前在里面的人去哪了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I want to know what happened to the man who was in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.29,0:31:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,没有我的批准  他不能被转移\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He can't be moved without my authorization.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.66,0:31:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉  但显然是可以的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm sorry, but, apparently, he can.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.50,0:31:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我真的很抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm truly sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.62,0:31:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我逼迫你陪我参加了这场愚蠢的不幸冒险\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that I manipulated you into accompanying me on this lame-brained misadventure.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.37,0:31:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我一定会澄清你没有参与策划计划\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I fully intend to make known that you had no role in planning my scheme
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.71,0:31:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,也没有参与计划的实施\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and no witting part in its execution.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.50,0:31:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我刚回城里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I just got back in town.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.21,0:31:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你俩怎么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What the hell, you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.96,0:31:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,罗曼·卡尔霍恩的身份完全属实\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, Roman Calhoun is exactly who he says he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.66,0:31:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,他是鲁比公司的管道工\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's a plumber at Ruby's.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.33,0:31:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,他们在文书上有点偷懒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They've been a little lazy with the paperwork,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.41,0:32:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,但他们的确与城市有合同\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but they do have a contract with the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.75,0:32:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,根据这张单据\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And, according to this invoice,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.33,0:32:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,在你看到卡尔霍恩先生的当晚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Calhoun was sent to Stephanie's building
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.54,0:32:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,他确实被派去了史蒂芬妮的大楼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}on the night you saw him there
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.75,0:32:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,修理工作区的水槽\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to fix a sink in a work area.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.79,0:32:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在他衣橱里发现的绑架工具包怎么说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But what about the kidnap kit we found in his closet?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.37,0:32:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,那些武器是非法的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Those weapons are illegal.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.21,0:32:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,对你们来说是非法的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}For you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.58,0:32:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,他是正式公民  他有执照的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's a full citizen. He has a license.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.54,0:32:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我们很多人都有应急包\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A lot of us have go bags,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.00,0:32:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,即使是住在这里很多年的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}even people who have been here for years.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.91,0:32:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我给卡尔霍恩说了你的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I told Calhoun your story,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.50,0:32:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,说了史蒂芬妮的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}told him about Stephanie,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.29,0:32:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,解释了你所经历的一切\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}explained everything you've been through,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.04,0:32:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,精神上受到的折磨\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the mental anguish that it's caused you,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.46,0:32:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,他同意不提出指控\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and he has agreed to not press charges.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.46,0:32:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,但你不能再骚扰他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But you have to leave him alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.75,0:32:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,签个字\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, and sign that.
