Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.71,0:35:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不过  我知道一个你不知道的信息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}However, I'm privy to one piece of data that you are not.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.08,0:35:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道那种感受\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I know how it felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.71,0:35:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Okay.
