Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.62,0:36:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不用每天都拼死拼活\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Not every day has to be a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.79,0:36:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,暂住在这里本来就该这样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's what moving here temporarily was supposed to be all about.
