Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.79,0:37:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,看最后一个名字\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Look at the last one.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.91,0:37:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}泰勒·戴维斯
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.50,0:39:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,就说我听到动静了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I told you I heard something.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.25,0:39:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我来处理\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.37,0:39:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你耍了我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You played me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.83,0:39:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我就知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.58,0:39:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你为卡尔霍恩的虚假不在场证明提供佐证\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You corroborated Calhoun's bogus alibi,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.04,0:39:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我很确定你参与了掩盖史蒂芬妮的失踪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I was certain you were involved with covering up Stephanie's disappearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.25,0:40:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,但我现在才意识到我的妄想有多严重\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But now I realize the depths of my self-delusion,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.25,0:40:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,因为在肚子上重重挨了一脚之前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}because Occam's razor should have led me to this conclusion
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.33,0:40:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我早该遵照奥卡姆剃刀定律得出最简单的结论\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}before a well-placed kick to the belly ever did.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.00,0:40:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,从来就没有什么史蒂芬妮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There was never any Stephanie.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.96,0:40:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,她是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Who is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.66,0:40:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,她是卧底特工吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Is she an undercover agent?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.62,0:40:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,欠你人情的欺诈师吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A con artist that owes you a favor?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.29,0:40:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,她演得太真了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, she was very convincing.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.79,0:40:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你利用她打动我的感情  骗我说出了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You used her to pull at my heartstrings and to trick me into telling you
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.71,0:40:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你想知道的关于我们社区的一切\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}everything you wanted to know about our communities.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.21,0:40:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你成功了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, it worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.21,0:40:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,她引我去了火车场\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}She led me to the train yard,
