Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.75,0:40:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你认为我好欺负\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You thought I wa-- you thought I was an easy mark,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.04,0:41:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,最信任警察\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the most trusting of the police, so you --
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.21,0:41:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你把我的朋友们一个个拆散\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}you split off my friends one at a time,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.12,0:41:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,以为我的防线会崩溃  但我没崩溃\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}thinking I'd break, but I didn't break.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.25,0:41:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,然后她引我去了无线电室  我们再次被抓\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Then she led me to the -- the radio room, where we were captured again.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.41,0:41:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,这次你倒是赚翻了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, and you certainly got your money's worth there.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.29,0:41:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我竟然上了两次当\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I actually fell for that one twice!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.91,0:41:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,她说我可以信任你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}She's the one that told me I can trust you!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.21,0:41:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,而我信任了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And I did.
