Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.54,0:41:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,以获取任何有用的自传式信息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}so that she could get any helpful autobiographical information
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.37,0:41:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,来满足你的需要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that might serve your needs!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.66,0:41:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,现在你得到了想要的一切  怎么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But now that you've gotten everything you wanted, what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.46,0:41:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,骗局没必要再继续了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No need to continue the ruse?!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.08,0:41:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是这样吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Is that it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.08,0:41:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,但你没料到这个反转\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But you didn't see this twist.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.79,0:41:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我一定会让所有人都知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I am gonna make absolutely certain that everybody knows
