Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.91,0:42:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.41,0:42:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,但谁会分那么清呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But who's keeping score, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.04,0:42:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,为了让你们来这里  我的确做了一些事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So, I did what I had to do to get you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.50,0:42:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,知道吗  你们应该为此感谢我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And you know what? You should be thanking me for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.50,0:42:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你们蠢到不知道天上掉了馅饼可不是我的错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's not my fault you people are too stupid to know a good thing when it landed in your laps.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.37,0:42:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你就直接承认了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're just -- you're just admitting it?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.00,0:42:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱上了她  而我所知的她的一切都是假象\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I fell in love, and everything I know about her is a fiction!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.46,0:42:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,当你动了真情时  我们试过让你面对现实\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Look, we tried to rip the Band-Aid off when we saw it was getting serious,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.58,0:43:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我用尽办法阻止你寻找她  但你就是不停手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and I did everything I could to get you to stop looking for her, but you wouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.41,0:43:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,结果闹成了这样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And here we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.54,0:43:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,至少你现在能停手了吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}At least you can stop now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.41,0:43:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,当时你们的情况不会好转  尤金\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It wasn't gonna get better for your people, Eugene.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.21,0:43:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,他们将会饿死\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They were about to starve.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.25,0:43:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,现在你们来了这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And now you're here
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.33,0:43:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你们的社区得到了修缮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and your community is getting fixed
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.29,0:43:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你们得到了一切  从音乐会到癌症手术\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and you've got everything, from concerts to cancer surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.71,0:43:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,而我们对你们的唯一要求\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And literally the only thing we've ever asked of you all in return
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.04,0:43:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,就是成为对这里有贡献的成员\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}is to be productive members of society here
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.62,0:43:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,只要你们自愿留下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}for as long as you choose to stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.37,0:43:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,所以  随心所欲地告诉他们吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So, tell them whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.00,0:43:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你为了出狱签的那份声明\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The statement you signed to get out of jail
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.29,0:43:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,上面写着你因神经焦虑导致了偏执\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}says you were suffering from paranoia as a result of nervous strain.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.37,0:43:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,记得吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.04,0:44:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,看看你  尤金\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I mean, look at you, Eugene.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.71,0:44:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,这显然对你打击很大\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This has obviously taken a toll.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.50,0:44:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你心碎了我遗憾吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Am I sorry your heart got broken?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.41,0:44:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,那当然\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.79,0:44:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信你的朋友们听说了一定也很难过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And I'm sure your friends will be very sad to hear about it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.21,0:44:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,但权衡一下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But in the balance of things,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.00,0:44:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我仍觉得这个结果对大家都好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I still think it worked out in everyone's favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.41,0:44:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,他们应该也会这样想\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And they probably would, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.91,0:44:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,对了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.79,0:44:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,顺便说句\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}By the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.75,0:44:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,史蒂芬妮的真名是席拉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Stephanie's real name is Shira.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.37,0:44:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,她讨厌铁娘子乐队\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And she hates Iron Maiden.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.66,0:44:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,但她真的很喜欢你的小说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But she genuinely enjoyed your book.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.96,0:44:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该继续写下去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You should stick with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.04,0:45:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,尤金\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Eugene?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.87,0:45:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你还好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.54,0:46:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,尤金  我要和你谈谈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Eugene, I need to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.62,0:46:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,土豆虫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Tater Bug.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.37,0:46:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,蓝象甲呼叫土豆虫  请回答\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is Blue Weevil to Tater Bug. Please come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.00,0:46:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.21,0:46:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,是我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.54,0:46:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我是在无线电里和你通话的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm the one you were talking to on the radio.

